{"tid":1655774,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中方感謝日方在貨輪沉沒事故中積極搜救和妥善處置","createTime":"2019-10-15T08:33:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T09:19:31.000Z","uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8717ab0ea87cbb54ce83608c90faf09581f5b4","tid":1655774,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:33:11.000Z","msg":"中方感謝日方在貨輪沉沒事故中積極搜救和妥善處置<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部發言人耿爽說，受風暴影響，一艘巴拿馬籍貨輪上星期六在日本神奈川縣附近海域沉沒，船上7名中國船員中1人獲救，6人死亡。耿爽說，事發後中國駐日本大使館，立即啓動應急機制，向日方核實有關情況和探望獲救船員，並為中國船員家屬善後，提供協助，中方感謝日方在事故中，積極搜救和妥善處置。<br />\n<br />\nrthk 2019-10-15 16:24:23"},{"pid":"ed79d863e33eccc828968ede468d28582359e135","tid":1655774,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:54:18.000Z","msg":"皇天擊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a5e7b2356b7d3ca7dd0cd200751625001d29cb","tid":1655774,"uid":36452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"又唔係唔知果度有風, 都照行, 唔規劃航程, 中共視人命如土介, 死不足惜, D貨緊要D, 照行, 最後連人帶貨沉沒大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3380d980df8f646a676977e22eb2f7715f3fbd5","tid":1655774,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3a5e7b2356b7d3ca7dd0cd200751625001d29cb","tid":1655774,"uid":36452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:04:46.000Z","msg":"又唔係唔知果度有風, 都照行, 唔規劃航程, 中共視人命如土介, 死不足惜, D貨緊要D, 照行, 最後連人帶貨沉沒大海<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"仲要浪費D人資源去拯救"},{"pid":"04b1a6bf4c455cfb2bffc3c2d9865de8721d2619","tid":1655774,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3380d980df8f646a676977e22eb2f7715f3fbd5","tid":1655774,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e3a5e7b2356b7d3ca7dd0cd200751625001d29cb","tid":1655774,"uid":36452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c